  "text": "In POEMS syndrome, specific immunocytochemistry study of myelinated fibers and of the endoneurium may be negative but electron microscopy can disclose uncompacted myelin lamellae (UML) which are characteristic features of this condition and may be visible in about 10% of the persisting myelinated fibers [CITATION_1] .",
